+   |
+13 |     tags: v*.*.*
+   |     ^~~~~
+test.yaml:15:3: unknown Webhook event "pullreq". see https://docs.github.com/en/actions/learn-github-actions/events-that-trigger-workflows#webhook-events for list of all Webhook event names [events]
+   |
+15 |   pullreq:
+   |   ^~~~~~~~
