+[Playground](https://rhysd.github.io/actionlint#eJxNjEEKAjEQBO95Rd8CygQ8mq+IQrJEg8jMsjPj+3Wzl5yaoooWzgFYXfu+QN0KL73pQQAhPp4iFAdbec3mezrHiW5XutxjCG+po7KmdtSbs5Jwhldnc/qU3Q2l1tbp819mtKULUko/10snvA==)
