+For filtering branches, tags and paths in Webhook events, [glob syntax][filter-pattern-doc] is available.
+actionlint validates glob patterns `branches:`, `branches-ignore:`, `tags:`, `tags-ignore:`, `paths:`, `paths-ignore:` in a
+workflow. It checks:
+
